{# 
  Macro: mark
  Purpose: Adds an icon indicating proficiency, expertise, or jack of all trades.
  Parameters:
  - prof: Proficiency status (1 if proficient, 0 otherwise).
  - exp: Expertise status (1 if expert, 0 otherwise).
  - pb: Proficiency bonus.
